# Windsurf Configuration for Nabda v2.0 Deployment

This configuration applies all v2.0 implementations automatically.

## What's Included

✅ Message personalization ({{name}}, {{governorate}}, {{category}})
✅ Safe error handling (no JSON crashes)
✅ Test mode (safe scaling)
✅ A/B testing framework
✅ AI follow-up assistant
✅ Webhook integration
✅ Improved UI/UX

## Files to Process

### Modified Files
- server.ts (personalization + error handling + webhooks)
- src/components/CampaignView.tsx (test mode + confirmations)
- src/components/TemplateEditor.tsx (better documentation)

### New Files
- src/lib/gemini-helper.ts (AI assistant)
- src/components/TemplateABTest.tsx (A/B testing)

## Build & Deploy

```bash
npm install
npm run build
git add .
git commit -m "Deploy: Nabda v2.0 - Personalization + AI + A/B Testing"
git push origin main
```

